OL,3,CRobert Peston: Is this Starmer's
OL,4,CWaterloo?
OL,6,FI understand Labour MP Catherine West
OL,7,Fwill press ahead with her stalking-
OL,8,Fhorse leadership challenge to the
OL,9,Fprime minister, though with a
OL,10,Fsignificant change, namely that he
OL,11,Fshould set a timetable for a change of
OL,12,Fleadership.
OL,14,FShe will email all Labour MPs about it
OL,15,Flater today. Keir Starmer's closest
OL,16,Fsupporters fear she will get enough
OL,17,Fsupport to ramp up pressure on him to
OL,18,Fset such a timetable. We shall see.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
