OL,3,CRobert Peston: Is this Starmer's
OL,4,CWaterloo?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe deficit, they say, was in respect
OL,12,Fof significant policy shifts. As one
OL,13,Fmember of the cabinet said to me,
OL,14,F"there was a promise that he would be
OL,15,Fradical, but he did not give details
OL,16,Fon anything new of substance."
OL,18,FAnd MPs have heard Starmer make
OL,19,Fambitious claims for "change" before
OL,20,Fthat have not been matched by deeds.
OL,26,@vD@AOUxD@^O]{D@VOU{D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
